cu.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an invalid value will cause ASN.1 parsing errors and prevent proper message encoding and decoding.

du.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an invalid value will cause ASN.1 parsing errors and prevent proper message encoding and decoding.
du.explanation_zh: 將 Asn1_verbosity 設定為無效值會導致 ASN.1 解析錯誤，並阻止正確的消息編碼和解碼。
